content:
We’re updating the obsolete Salesforce API Only Systems Integration user profile from a standard to a custom profile. This allows you to delete the profile in orgs where it exists.

The Salesforce API Only Systems Integration user profile was replaced with the more secure Minimum Access - API Only Integrations user profile in the Spring ‘24 release. 

This update is available in Enterprise, Unlimited, Performance, and Developer editions.
title: Updating Salesforce API User Profile
